      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; dimensional similarity between validation and COU geometries is documented in the similarity rationale.",
      "rationale": "Equivalency of input parameters between validation configuration and COU is addressed qualitatively in VAL-SIM-001. Formal equivalency assessment is not required at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4-1."
    }
